parameters:
Underling: L-Lord Shark Duke... are you alright...? This is
a terrible situation...

Memimi: ...Y-you guys... Everyone's been captured by Mayor
Orca Asparagus... I'm sorry... It's because I lost...

Mayor Orca Asparagus: Sha-sha~! Those among Shark Broccoli's
underlings who dared to defy me have been captured and
imprisoned here!

Mayor Orca Asparagus: If you say you'll become my
subordinate, I'll release you anytime... But if you refuse,
I'll torment you right here along with Shark Duke!

Underling: Lord Shark Duke... I'm so sorry...! All of us
tried to avenge the great leader Shark Broccoli, but we were
beaten back... and to make matters worse, many have turned
traitor...

Memimi: I'm sorry... ugh... I'm proud of you all... But I
don't blame those who turned their backs...

Memimi: For now, please think of yourselves first... I can't
do anything for you anymore... *sob*... sorry... forgive
me... ugh...
Underling: L-Lord Shark Duke...!! Damn it... *sniffle*...

Mayor Orca Asparagus: Sha-sha-sha... You want to save these
guys, right? Shark Duke! Alright then~ If you can complete
the tasks in my AV project, I'll let them go!!

Underling: N-No, Lord Shark Duke!! It's bound to be a rotten
project... You can't do such a thing for our sake!!

Underling: Please don't appear in any more AVs!! Forget
about us and just get out of this muddy city...

Even if her spirit is broken by repeated humiliation, Memimi
remains the Shark Duke... It's her way of life to endure
anything for her comrades. Despite trembling with fear,
words of consent involuntarily escape her lips...

Underling: When I joined the organization, I thought
unifying the city was impossible, but thanks to Lord Shark
Broccoli's efforts, it's starting to feel real. If you never
forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: You must never give up on your dreams... I will
continue to fight as many times as necessary to achieve my
goal. You all should just believe in me and Lord Shark
Broccoli, the great boss, and follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, the fact that I got to see Lord Shark
Broccoli's numerous lewd forms was like a dream come true...
The camera in the shower room has been removed, but I've
saved recordings for days and watched them over and over...
Even though I know it's wrong, there's no way I can delete
the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: To think the mayor would show up... I never
imagined it! That bastard, acting so brazenly...! And if we
lose, Lord Shark Broccoli making an AV debut of all things!!
I really want to see it, but the nerve...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a personal gift from me! I bought it
with my own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As
someone involved in the powder refining business, I can't
let the recipe fall into the wrong hands no matter what...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. This powder, Lord Shark Broccoli's masterpiece, I
won't hand it over to anyone...

You ate the nutritious powder and felt energized! Max HP
increased by 50!

Underling: Was it three years ago that Lord Shark Broccoli
was picked up by the boss? This organization was founded
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The boss initially didn't intend to bring me into
the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with what
happened at that time... I joined the organization a year
ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's a rapid rise... Now, Lord Shark Broccoli
has become one of the most important figures in the dark
organization, on the verge of unifying the city... Seriously
amazing...

Memimi: The one I must repay isn't just Lord Shark
Broccoli... It's also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and sometimes guided me. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I could ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! Damn
it... I've been exposing my shame to close acquaintances...
My relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Mountain-san loses and has
to make an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I
want her to be only mine... I do want to see her having sex,
but I don't want her to do it with anyone other than me...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV raping a celebrity in reverse, I felt like I was going to
lose it, and now to think she has to sleep around with other
men as a matter of routine... it does get me a bit hard,
but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel
but...

Underling: At least, take this...! It's a heart-shaped
necklace that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor
Orca...!!

Memimi: Gross... no, I mean... uh, I'll just accept the
sentiment... thank you...

With the underling's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...
